com.serena.dmclient.objects
Interface ItemTypeGroup

All Superinterfaces:
DimensionsObject
public interface ItemTypeGroup
extends DimensionsObject

Represents a Dimensions Item Type Group.

An item type group is used to define a collection of item types that can be used in a release template.

Note: Item type groups are defined at a global (base database) level and are not associated with a specific product. A Dimensions product is only used to restrict the list of item types when defining a new group, or editing the details of an existing one.
